data.description: Bring an offer to this beautiful, upgraded new home in desirable Cowley Crossing. Raised ranch with 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms. Centrally located with a quick commute to Fort Knox, Blue Oval SK, NuCor and easy access to I65. An abundance of space with an open/split floor plan. On the main level you will find a well appointed kitchen with upgraded stainless appliances, stainless hood vent, large island, granite countertops and pantry. Also, a spacious living/dining area, two secondary bedrooms, guest bathroom and the primary bedroom with a walk-in closet and an en-suite that will wow you with a beautiful roomy tile shower, stand alone tub and duel vanity. You will be pleased to see so much extra living space on the lower level, large multipurpose area, full bathroom, large bedroom and laundry room with cabinet and countertop space. Fully fenced backyard. Enjoy your favorite morning beverage while taking in the beautiful sunrise on your back deck and at the end of the day you can witness inspiring sunsets from the front of the house. Schedule a showing and fall in love before someone else does.
